data.title: The Gods of Mars (Barsoom #2)
data.meta_description: The classic book, The Gods of Mars by Edgar Rice Burroughs There's a reason why The Gods of Mars is one of the best books of all time. If you haven't read this classic, then you'd better pick up a copy of The Gods of Mars by Edgar Rice Burroughs today.
